articles.author: Adam Haigh
articles.title: Westpac Bank Increases Dividend, Will Buy Back $980 Million - Bloomberg
articles.description: Westpac Banking Corp. lifted its dividend and said it will buy back A$1.5 billion ($980 million) of its own shares, offering investors some respite to the intense competition in the Australian mortgage market that’s testing profitability.
